此文件用于 Song App 的说明：
首先，感谢您使用我设计的 Song App Version 6.1，接下来是对此的详细说明：
目录是一份菜单，包含选项1-9，共9个功能：1、添加歌曲；2、更新歌曲；3、删除歌曲；4、列出所有歌曲；5、搜索歌曲；6、搜索歌手；7、获取音乐排行榜；8、播放歌曲；9、将歌曲列表发送到指定邮箱。
其中，功能5、6、7未能实现，原因见下详细说明。
1、添加歌曲：起始为空专辑空歌曲，默认先添加一张专辑，再向其添加一首歌曲，每次只能添加一首歌曲（专辑不能单独操作，一旦添加则不能修改或删除）。
2、更新歌曲：选择一首歌曲后进行数据的修改，如果不想修改某项可以按回车键跳过。
3、删除歌曲：选择一首歌后进行删除（此操作不能撤销）。
4、列出所有歌曲：将专辑和歌曲的最新结果打印出来。
5、搜索歌曲：爬取豆瓣网音乐平台进行搜索（功能尚未实现，我尝试加入很多的 header，甚至使用 API 密钥，也不能爬取到数据内容，顶多爬取到网页前端 HTML 布局内容，可能是豆瓣网音乐平台为了保护服务器，设置了严密的反爬虫系统，也可能是我技术不精）。
6、搜索歌手：爬取豆瓣网音乐平台进行搜索（功能尚未实现，原因见上）。
7、获取音乐排行榜：爬取豆瓣网音乐平台进行搜索（功能尚未实现，原因见上）。
8、播放歌曲：根据菜单指引，选择一首歌进行播放（javax.sound.midi 音乐库）。
9、将歌曲列表发送到指定邮箱：根据菜单指引，输入指定人的 QQ 账号，将邮件发送到指定人的 QQ 邮箱。
注意：运行选项8的时候，读取文件的时候请不要按回车键，否则再次运行选项8的时候会导致重复播放。
我对 controllers 类和 models 类拟写了 test 类测试文件，其中有部分错误，由于时间问题，未能及时修正，请谅解。
由于我的水平有限，文件中可能还会含有其他错误，请谅解。
参考资料：《Java 从入门到精通》、git hub（MIDI 音乐制作）、优课达官网（爬取音乐相关内容）。
最后，再次感谢您使用我设计的 Song App，祝您工作顺利、生活愉快！
开发者：樊心康。

This file is used for the description of Song App:
First of all, thank you for using the Song App Version 6.1 I designed. Next is a detailed description of it:
The directory is a menu, including options 1-9, with a total of 9 functions: 1. Add songs; 2. Update songs; 3. Delete songs; 4. List all songs; 5. Search for songs; 6. Search for singers; 7. Get music rankings; 8. Play songs; 9. Send the song list to the designated mailbox.
Among them, functions 5, 6 and 7 failed to be realized. The reasons are explained in detail below.
1. Add songs: start with an empty album and empty songs. By default, add an album first, and then add a song to it. Only one song can be added at a time (the album cannot be operated alone, and once added, it cannot be modified or deleted).
2. Update the song: Select a song and modify the data. If you don't want to modify an item, you can press the Enter key to skip it.
3. Delete the song: Select a song and delete it (this operation cannot be undored).
4. List all the songs: print out the latest results of the album and songs.
5. Search for songs: crawl the Douban.com music platform to search (the function has not been realized yet. I tried to add a lot of headers. Even using the API key, I can't crawl the data content. At most, I crawl to the front-end HTML layout content of the web page. Maybe the Douban.com music platform is in order to protect Protect the server and set up a strict anti-crawler system, which may also be my lack of skills).
6. Search for singers: crawl the Douban.com music platform to search (the function has not been realized yet, the reason is as above).
7. Get the music ranking list: crawl the Douban music platform to search (the function has not been realized yet, the reason is as above).
8. Play songs: According to the menu guidelines, select a song to play (javax.sound.midi music library).
9. Send the song list to the designated mailbox: According to the menu guidelines, enter the QQ account of the designated person and send the email to the QQ mailbox of the designated person.
Note: When running option 8, please do not press Enter when reading the file, otherwise it will cause repeated playback when running option 8 again.
I wrote a test file for the controllers class and the models class. There are some errors in it. Due to time problems, it could not be corrected in time. Please understand.
Due to my limited level, there may be other errors in the file. Please understand.
Reference materials: "Java from Introduction to Proficiency", git hub (MIDI music production), Youkeda official website (crawling music-related content).
Finally, thank you again for using the Song App I designed. I wish you a smooth work and a happy life!
Developer: Fan Xinkang.